videos.description: Marial Shayok uses the shot fake to get space, then knocks down the triple for the Cyclones.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Shayok hits the tough 3-pointer for Iowa State) 2019/01/08

videos.headline: Shayok hits the tough 3-pointer for Iowa State

videos.description: Lindell Wigginton gets out in transition for the Cyclones and somehow is able to get the shot to go down while falling to the ground.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Iowa State's Wigginton hits and-1 shot while falling) 2019/01/08

videos.headline: Iowa State's Wigginton hits and-1 shot while falling

videos.description: Makai Mason hits a deep trey, his fourth 3-pointer of the game, for Baylor.
videos.headline: Mason heating up from deep for Baylor

videos.description: Iowa State's Nick Weiler-Babb draws a lot of contact from Baylor's Makai Mason, but no foul is issued and the Bears hold on to win.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Baylor wins after no-call on Iowa State's final shot) 2019/01/08 ESHEET

videos.headline: Baylor wins after no-call on Iowa State's final shot
